dct_title_s: Map of Eastern Persia to illustrate the paper by Major General Sir F. J. Goldsmid
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. The Author's Route shown in red. Established and conjectural lines of the Persian Frontier (boundary) are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 43 (1873), pp. 65-83; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 43 1873
